#######################################
## Default if not given above
Host *
    ForwardAgent yes
    KeepAlive yes
    ServerAliveCountMax 10
    ServerAliveInterval 120
    ForwardX11 no
    ForwardX11Trusted yes
    ForwardX11Timeout 7d
    AddKeysToAgent yes
    UseKeychain yes
